name: Gold Floral Sparkle iPad case
description:
This dark sparkle embroidery iPad case is a collaboration with the US based company, Keka Case. 

A tapestry floral inspired design, available for the iPad 2/3/4 and iPad mini.

This handcrafted case is akin to a hardback book cover and is made using eco-friendly inks. With its dreamy and pastel coloured design, it's a fantastic way to update your accessory and makes a special gift for a loved one this Christmas.

This case for the iPad also doubles as a stand in landscape mode and can be propped up easily to watch films or to show slideshows.

Stain and tear resistant.

Christmas gift? Let us know and we will gift wrap it in gold tissue. We can also include personalised messages and sent it to the gift recipient directly.
